translations: 北西北（north-northwest）；国民福利指标（Net National Welfare）

sentences.sentence: For you to say NNW is extreme!
sentences.translation: 你得说在西北方向偏北太极端了！

sentences.sentence: I noticed the sun setting in the NNW location. I haven't been able to observe the sunrise.
sentences.translation: 我注意到太阳在西北方向偏北的位置，我还没有看见过日出。

sentences.sentence: The newly formed Tengchong Jinghong NNW zone and Dali Chuxiong NWW zone have an important role in the block division.
sentences.translation: 指出新生的腾冲-景洪北北西带和大理-楚雄北西西带在活动地块划分中的重要作用。
